::KitKat::

She looked at Aracnia. "I wasn't expecting you to be here Aracnia. 
Very well." She looked at Megatron. "I have asked you to sit on our 
council. The HIGh PREDACON COUNCIL that I am making here. You will 
take a seat and govern over your own group, but we will al help each 
other. What do you say to this?"


The clone of Megatron looked down and growled a low growl at 
NightEyes. "Leave KitKat's quarters now," is said to her.
